# Real-Time Collaborative Editor

A simple collaborative note-taking tool built using:
- Express.js
- Socket.io (WebSocket)
- HTML/CSS/JS

## Features
- Real-time text sync between users
- Lightweight frontend
- Built on WebSocket via Socket.io

## Setup

```bash
npm install
node server.js

Visit: http://localhost:3000

